]
synopsis:
  "This is a legacy version of the Sail language to support RMEM, and should not be used elsewhere"
description:
  """Sail is a language for describing the instruction-set
architecture (ISA) semantics of processors. This is a legacy version
to support RMEM and should not be used elsewhere. Use the "sail" package instead."""
